('prt_f83da001d001ocDi1WZV25TnIu', 'msg_f83d9f9bf001h8ZnveDvxmkdXg', 'ses_0a9dac278ffeGqD1mzTDArbRM0', 1784623530013, 1784623531290, '{"type":"reasoning","text":"用户要我帮他组织一段英文回复，回复给 GitHub issue 上的讨论。需要涵盖：\n1. 说明自己的 skill 和 tranhailong 的需求不同\n2. 说明自己的 skill 解决的是什么问题\n3. 语气要礼貌、简洁\n4. 用中文思考，但输出英文回复","time":{"start":1784623530013,"end":1784623531289}}'),
('prt_f83da051b001drfw4l7SnFCwX4', 'msg_f83d9f9bf001h8ZnveDvxmkdXg', 'ses_0a9dac278ffeGqD1mzTDArbRM0', 1784623531291, 1784623536582, '{"type":"text","text":"Here''s a draft reply:\n\n---\n\nThanks @tranhailong for the context! I think our use cases are actually different:\n\n- **Your scenario**: Continue a coding session on a mobile device, which requires opencode''s server-side native support for real-time cross-device sync (project list + session list).\n- **My skill**: A developer-side solution for **full database-level backup and migration between dev machines** (e.g., work desktop ↔ laptop) via git. It requires git + Node.js, so it''s not suitable for mobile use.\n\nThese two are complementary rather than overlapping:\n\n1. **Server-side sync** (what you''re requesting) is needed for lightweight, real-time access across any device including mobile — this needs to be built into opencode itself.\n2. **My skill** solves a different problem: complete conversation data portability between machines as SQL backups, with full database fidelity (all tables, relationships intact), path-agnostic placeholder substitution, dry-run preview, and zero external dependencies. It''s designed for developers who want git-managed conversation archives, not for resuming sessions on the go.\n\nThat said, if opencode eventually ships native cross-device sync, my skill could still serve as a local backup/export tool — similar to how you''d want both cloud sync and local backups for important data.\n\n---\n\n需要调整语气或内容可以告诉我。","time":{"start":1784623531291,"end":1784623536581}}'),
('prt_f83da1ac9001dpEAlShz2GZFue', 'msg_f83d9f9bf001h8ZnveDvxmkdXg', 'ses_0a9dac278ffeGqD1mzTDArbRM0', 1784623536841, 1784623536842, '{"reason":"stop","snapshot":"07d86c9c52de24a350cb79ee216f5b865b9b85c8","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":20996,"input":1567,"output":291,"reasoning":66,"cache":{"write":0,"read":19072}},"cost":0.0028081}'),
