('prt_f560465390016rgJRMZck0nuvY', 'msg_f56045e2100116pqRNYls9AiRO', 'ses_0a9fbb56effeQaZdXvhiM6xltc', 1783854556473, 1783854562848, '{"type":"reasoning","text":"Now I understand what this skill does. It''s an opencode skill for backing up and importing conversation records between devices. The conversation data is exported as SQL files and managed via git.\n\nLet me think of some good project names for open-sourcing this:\n\nKey aspects:\n- It''s for opencode (the CLI tool)\n- It backs up/exports and imports conversation history\n- It uses git for sync across devices\n- It''s a \"skill\" for opencode\n\nName ideas:\n1. `opencode-conversation-backup` - descriptive but long\n2. `opencode-sync` - concise, implies syncing conversations\n3. `opencode-backup` - simple\n\n\n4. `oc-conversation-backup` - abbreviated\n5. `opencode-migrate` - implies migration\n6. `opencode-history-sync` - descriptive\n\nSince this is an opencode skill, I should follow the naming convention of similar skills like `find-skills` and `skill-creator`. I''m leaning toward `opencode-conversation-backup` for clarity, though `opencode-sync` is more concise and captures the cross-device sync aspect better.\n\nLooking at this more carefully, it''s really functioning as both a backup and import tool, so I''m considering names like `opencode-conversation-sync` to emphasize the bidirectional nature, or `opencode-history-backup` to be more explicit about what''s being managed. The shortest option, `opencode-sync`, is appealing but might be too vague. I think I''ll go with `opencode-conversation-sync` as the strongest choice—it''s clear, concise, and accurately reflects the two-way functionality.","time":{"start":1783854556473,"end":1783854562847}}'),
('prt_f56047e21001HlHHB7qeRmnu1l', 'msg_f56045e2100116pqRNYls9AiRO', 'ses_0a9fbb56effeQaZdXvhiM6xltc', 1783854562849, 1783854565367, '{"type":"text","text":"几个建议，按推荐顺序：\n\n| 名称 | 理由 |\n|------|------|\n| **opencode-conversation-sync** | 准确描述核心功能（跨设备同步对话），简洁易记 |\n| **opencode-history-backup** | 强调\"历史记录备份\"，语义直观 |\n| **opencode-sync** | 最短，但含义偏泛 |\n| **oc-conversation-backup** | 保留原名辨识度，`oc` 前缀表明是 opencode 生态 |\n\n推荐 **`opencode-conversation-sync`** — 既体现了备份又体现了导入（双向同步），且符合 opencode 生态命名风格。","time":{"start":1783854562849,"end":1783854565366}}'),
